{"tid":527235,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"列台港為國　明報南華早報聯合航空捲風波","createTime":"2018-01-12T12:29:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T16:28:39.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"93c45ecc46cc86e9c58608ca01481bf16e72698c","tid":527235,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T12:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180112/photo/bkn-20180112161513294-0112_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180112202741\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180112%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180112161513294-0112_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180112202741&h=f5400030&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n繼內地發現萬豪酒店集團的網站將中國大陸與台灣同列「國家」後，東網亦發現兩間航空司及兩間本地傳媒機構有同類情況。聯合航空美國及香港的官方網頁在供客購買機票時，將台灣列作「國家」的選項之一，而聯合航空香港的網站內，「帳單地址國家」的中英文頁面均顯示，「台灣」及「中國」均屬國家。<br />\n<br />\n至於母公司為海航集團的香港快運，其流動應用程式內的個人資料，護照發行國家一欄中，有「台灣」與中國的選項。暫未知兩間航空公司會否與萬豪「同一命運」，遭內地部門勒令「封網整頓」。<br />\n<br />\n除航空公司，個別香港傳媒機構的網站亦將香港視作「國家」的情況。其中，在明報網站會員專區，用家登入後可更改個人檔案及聯絡資料，當中在「國家」選項，除有香港可供選擇，台灣及西藏亦是「國家」之一。至於南華早報網站的「我的帳戶」內，用家可選擇的國家(Country)亦包括香港，而台灣雖然亦是選項之一，但有附註指為中國的一省(Province of China)。<br />\n<br />\n經東網查詢後，明報在傍晚時更新「國家」一欄選項改為「國家/地區」，並於7時在其網站發表聲明道歉。<br />\n<br />\n香港快運表示，其流動應用程式簡體版經已納用了「台灣地區」字眼，現正統一所有語言版面旳用字。<br />\n<br />\n萬豪酒店早前在問卷上將港澳台及西藏，與中國大陸並列作「國家」。事件引發官媒及網民批評，當局已對萬豪集團立案調查，國家旅遊局等部門要求查明事件。上海市網信辦昨已勒令萬豪集團的官方中文網站、中文版APP自行關閉一周，全面自查整改，徹底清理違法違規訊息。"},{"pid":"b6da6e186efcaba3cb1c765e6c22207183e90015","tid":527235,"uid":550,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T13:20:08.000Z","msg":"土豆Youku淘寶夠將港澳台剔出國內啦<br />\n幾時要受罰呀"},{"pid":"4ce2261388ca20bd330a5bee1560d8beeb356cbd","tid":527235,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T13:48:23.000Z","msg":"支那玻璃心搞文字獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7f5535615184bb8baac5a2b9deff0775519e52f","tid":527235,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T13:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a08d23e816c28cb1c36ac503d2f21fbfe3bf36cd","tid":527235,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T13:58:18.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e1865533becc60f51a57c0512d9be8f2f768b8","tid":527235,"uid":20815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:04:50.000Z","msg":"美國搞簽證都係分開港澳台，又唔嘈下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ddde1862348e5a3f3916e654da552d2588fcb0","tid":527235,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:22:37.000Z","msg":"咩鳩野風波吖<br />\n大把跨國公司都係Country: Hong Kong咁係個List入面<br />\n夠僵你就杯葛全球 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d0abf69c175a09ca1e6421f64feeef4ad01fcc6","tid":527235,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:24:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美國搞簽證都係分開港澳台，又唔嘈下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最好封鎖埋個網站唔俾支那人搞簽證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98846e23048ed0cbc100fd05bfcc6a7b5389fd3a","tid":527235,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:26:32.000Z","msg":"垃圾國家"},{"pid":"e0efca79ca17f3a2775aa17eb3ed0909162f4b68","tid":527235,"uid":15815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:31:31.000Z","msg":"得啦知啦<br />\n好撚煩呀支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkg